Companion (bottom-screen training): extend the open-signal patch to stream the training session
(NPC name, player gold, best-3 skills with cost + capped flag) and add extern "C" control bridges
(companionTrainSkill / companionTrainingCancel) driven from drainCompanionCommands, mirroring
companion-repair-export.patch. COMPANION_TRAINING_CLOSED is emitted from every close path (onClose
real-close, exit() for B/Escape, the cancel bridge, and the post-train auto-close in
onTrainingFinished) because the window is DS-hidden and the normal visible->hidden onClose won't fire.
Prices come from getBarterOffer (native-only). Training is one-shot (auto-closes after a 2h advance),
so no re-export. Added July 2026.

